    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 20 secs on high or until warmed through</p><p>Combine your<strong> mayo</strong> with your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl – this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
